{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Here's the prompt to give Shopify AI:
    
    ---
    
    > Create a custom section called "Trust Badges" or "Store Features". It should have a light gray background color (hex #F5F5F5). The section displays 3 feature items in a single horizontal row, evenly spaced across the full width with generous padding on all sides.
    >
    > Each feature item has: a dark green outlined circular icon on the left (like a badge/seal icon, a box/returns icon, or a delivery truck icon — use SVG outline style icons, not filled), and to the right of the icon, a bold dark charcoal heading (like "Best price", "Easy Returns", "Fast shipping") with a smaller gray description paragraph below it. The icon and text should be vertically centered with each other.
    >
    > The background color of the section is light gray (#F5F5F5). The icon circles should have a dark green outline color (hex #1D5C3A) with the icon inside also in the same dark green. The heading text should be dark charcoal (hex #1A1A1A) and the description text should be medium gray (hex #555555).
    >
    > Each feature item's icon, heading text, and description text should all be editable from the theme editor. Allow up to 4 feature items and a minimum of 1. On mobile, the 3 items should stack vertically in a single column, each with the icon and text side by side.
    
    ---
    
    **Bonus tip** — add this for icon flexibility:
    
    > Allow me to choose the icon for each feature item from a set of common ecommerce icons (badge/seal, box, truck, lock, heart, star, clock, leaf) via a dropdown in the theme editor, so I don't need to upload custom images., Create a custom section called "Trust Badges". It should have a light gray background color (hex #F5F5F5) with top and bottom padding of 20px. Display 5 trust badge items in a single horizontal row, evenly spaced across the full width.
    Each badge item has a dark green outlined circular icon (hex #1D5C3A) on the left and text to the right. Use these exact 5 badges in this order:
    
    Shield/checkmark icon — heading "Secure Payment", description "100% secure & encrypted checkout"
    Refresh/return arrows icon — heading "Easy Returns", description "30-day hassle-free return policy"
    Delivery truck icon — heading "Fast Shipping", description "Free shipping on orders over $50"
    Ribbon/medal icon — heading "Best Price", description "Guaranteed unbeatable prices always"
    Headset/support icon — heading "24/7 Support", description "Dedicated support team always available"
    
    The icon circles should be outlined style (not filled) in dark green (#1D5C3A). Heading text in bold dark charcoal (#1A1A1A), description in medium gray (#555555). Each item's icon, heading, and description should be editable from the theme editor. On mobile, display 2 items per row and wrap to the next line, keeping icon and text side by side within each item.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-trust-badges-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_vertical }}px 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-trust-badges-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.padding_horizontal }}px;
  }

  .ai-trust-badges-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.item_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    border: {{ block.settings.icon_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: calc({{ block.settings.icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    height: calc({{ block.settings.icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    stroke: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-trust-badge-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-trust-badges-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.mobile_gap }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-trust-badges-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

